{"tid":2127611,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"外來惡鬼 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-07-27T11:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T12:18:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"14fdde2d9975528d1e1715f41ff0c602bfb6bae6","tid":2127611,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200727/20963805/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200727%2F20963805%2F&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=8b458988\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200727%2F20963805%2F&h=9c661503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20200727/20963805/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n外來惡鬼 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200727/large/1595749244_49a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200727%2Flarge%2F1595749244_49a4.jpg&h=dc10701e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七月十一日，新香港長官鄭月娥出席一教育論壇，痛言教育必須整頓：「國民教育、佔領中環、《逃犯條例》修訂等事件，使人清楚看見有反中央勢力滲透校園。」七月十三日，中共駐港辦公室見民主派立法會初選投票者多達六十一萬，也嚴詞譴責說：「反對派少數人獲外部勢力支持，籌辦『初選』，嚴重破壞選舉公平&hellip;&hellip;」中共駐港辦公室與鄭月娥所論事雖不同，卻同樣以「外部勢力滲透」為言，發人深省。<br />\n<br />\n其實那些外部勢力，當局既已「清楚看見」，為什麼不利用「國安法」這柄尚方寶劍，「揪出來」正法，卻不斷拘捕民主派中人及教師、學生？假如那些反中亂港的外國政府無法「揪出來」，乾脆與之斷交好了，為什麼還向他們反覆剖說「合則兩利，鬥則兩傷」之類國際大義？<br />\n<br />\n去年，臺灣傳出一段新聞：桃園市有神棍黃睿平者，貪一女大學生姿色，於是搖唇鼓舌，說她惡鬼纏身，要脫光衣服，任其魚肉，以驅除那股邪惡外來勢力。。。。。。。。。。。。。。但我由「反中亂港勢力」談到「某鬼某神為祟」，扯得未免太遠了。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"3321fa265a4b330b1e64acdc7cc049b20f7b5076","tid":2127611,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T12:18:29.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}